window.bookSummaryJSON = "<b><i>Bestseller in Hard Science Fiction! Bestseller in Science Fiction Adventure!</i></b><br><b>In the dark heart of an ancient city, an even darker secret is waiting.</b><br>On a rugged frontier world, ex-soldier Booker takes a job providing security for a high-stakes archaeological dig. The goal: to decode the inscriptions of a long-dead civilization. The problem: giant scorpions lurking in the caverns, and they're far more deadly than anyone realized.<br>When a savage attack on a brilliant young linguist forces Booker to confront the horrors of the underground ruins, he uncovers a chilling truth: the city hides a secret that could change the future of humanity forever.<br>Now, Booker must protect his team from the deadly creatures—and from enemies within his own people—before the past’s dark power falls into the wrong hands.<br><b>Perfect for fans of <i>The Expanse</i>, <i>Indiana Jones</i>, and <i>Pitch Black</i>, this sci-fi thriller delivers gritty action, ancient mysteries, and a relentless alien menace.</b>"; 
